snippet.title: Nintendo Switch Sports - Run This House - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Bring the thrill of different sports to life right in your home with Nintendo Switch Sports. Only on Nintendo Switch! ESRB Rating: EVERYONE 10+ with Mild Violence.

Nintendo Switch Sports is available April 29. Pre-order now: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/nintendo-switch-sports-switch/
